Commands:
  run        Run the daily pipeline and rebuild the review bundle
  review     Open the legislative review CLI
  apply      Apply approved legislative actions, rerun affected bills if needed, rebuild bundle
  import     Import approved tracked-bill seed rows and rebuild bundle
  feedback   Refresh feedback analysis and rebuild bundle

Legacy shortcuts still supported:
  equitystack run
  equitystack review
  equitystack apply
  equitystack import
  equitystack feedback
EOF
}

